{"tid":1545132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［必睇］假義載、真抽水名單","createTime":"2019-09-05T21:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T21:56:21.000Z","uid":313463,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1def52dd757a2d6486ae1ed1fb78ea582d86a353","tid":1545132,"uid":313463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:27:46.000Z","msg":"近日有傳有人假借義載之名，對女義士造出不軌、性侵嘅行為，我呼籲所有參與運動嘅義士們，不論係男係女，請提高警覺，喺上車之前要記低該車嘅車牌，同埋記清楚事發經過，以方便大家可協助你哋，將一切不法之徒繩之於法、追究到底、起佢全家底、再咀咒埋佢三代，務求以一切手段將佢哋清算，唔會比你哋白白受委屈<br />\n <br />\n對付假義載人士方法：（歡迎加插）<br />\n<br />\n1. 起晒佢底，搵晒佢所有嘅前度出嚟，然後叫佢啲前度爆晒佢啲私人事同醜事出嚟，然後再製成影片一併交畀《蘋果》，將佢嘅醜事話晒畀全世界知，等佢一世抬唔撚起頭做人，溝唔撚到女"},{"pid":"46286f2d7ef128b64dc199fa9a9819aefd7e6605","tid":1545132,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:28:00.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6598dc53bb8c6e914d0e1a347f1511c0a096e4c","tid":1545132,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T21:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n907 機場攻略正式出爐，唔使再驚大逃走！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544251</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84HxphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=e20ea5c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyo